name: Unidentified_Coruscant_Guard_1_(Florrum)
content: A clone trooper served as a shock trooper with the Coruscant Guard. He was part of a group of clone troopers led by Clone Commander CC-5869 "Stone" that accompanied Senator Kharrus and Junior Representative Jar Jar Binks to the planet Florrum, a group that was sent to negotiate the ransom to free Jedi Generals Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker from the Ohnaka Gang. However, a group of Hondo Ohnaka's men shot down their shuttle, killing Kharrus and the pilots. This trooper survived the crash and assumed that Commander Stone was meant to lead the group from there, and was surprised to hear that Representative Binks was the highest ranking member of their party. He, along with the others, were skeptical about Binks's ability to lead the group. However, each member of the group went on to survive and complete the mission.
